```

## Development

### Setup
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/aswhitehouse/open-agent-spec.git
cd oas-cli

# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Running Tests
```bash
pytest
```

### Building
```bash
python -m build
```

